"{\"uid\": \"forbes.com-sites-michellebruton-2024-05-19-jagger-eaton-makes-skateboarding-history-at-olympic-qualifier-series\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByMichelle Bruton, Contributor.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 32, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruton\", \"score\": 0.9991881009128751, \"rank\": 0.0008104112933946443, \"text\": \"Bruton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Contributor\", \"from\": 19, \"to\": 30}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leading up to the Paris 2024 Olympics, American skateboarder Jagger Eaton has a singular focus: to make history by becoming the first skateboarder not only to compete in both disciplines (street and park) at a single Games, but to make the podium in each.\", \"from\": 34, \"to\": 289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 73, \"end\": 81, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995644821055335, \"rank\": 0.00043495040597829165, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jagger_Eaton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jagger Eaton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jagger_Eaton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jagger_Eaton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 71}, {\"ngram\": \"a singular focus\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 128}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 145}, {\"ngram\": \"the first skateboarder\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 180}, {\"ngram\": \"both disciplines\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 220}, {\"ngram\": \"street\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"park\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"a single Games\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 256}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well,you might be thinking,skateboarding has only been in the Olympics once before, so how historic is this goal?While this is true, what Eaton hopes to accomplish is a rarity for the entire competitive skateboarding landscape, Olympics or otherwise.\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eaton_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.491517842284915e-17, \"text\": \"Eaton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eaton_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eaton_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 361}, {\"ngram\": \"this goal?While\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"a rarity\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire competitive skateboarding landscape\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding is not constructed to enable athletes to compete in multiple disciplines.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple disciplines\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many times, events will schedule practice for park during the street final, and vice versa.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"park\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eaton's goal requires hard work and resilience, not to mention help with logistics.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eaton_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.4