ing\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The points athletes earn in Shanghai, combined with their world ranking heading into the event and with whatever points they may earn at the second OQS event in Budapest in June, contribute toward Olympic qualification.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 0.7794423074135168, \"rank\": 0.28291280690018894, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\"}, {\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.999593036954979, \"rank\": 0.000407128729298347, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The points\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever points\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"the second OQS event\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic qualification\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the U.S. Olympic Skateboarding Team, qualification scores will be weighted by 33.3% World Skate Ranking 2022-May 2024, 33.3% OQS Shanghai and 33.3% OQS Budapest.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4377544662179072e-14, \"text\": \"Skateboarding\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\"}, {\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1703